    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Opisthotropis durandi spec. nov., paratype (IEBR A. 2013.26), alive in its natural biotope, Mok Waterfall, at about 4 km east of Ban Sopkhong, Ngoi District, Louangphabang Province, Laos. Photograph by Alexandre Teynié." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248428/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248429>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Map showing the type locality (black circle) of Opisthotropis durandi in Louangphabang Province, Laos." ;
